{"tid":2195060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：三權分立常用於主權國家　不適用於香港特區","createTime":"2020-09-09T02:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T05:45:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5abe05442c13fb327400bb6c60e83db69d6f17d7","tid":2195060,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司司長鄭若驊在報章撰文指，三權分立常用於形容主權國家的政治架構，並不適用於香港特區。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊表示，在沒有全面理解《基本法》和憲制秩序的情況下，任何人試圖將這個概念簡單化並套用於香港特區是枉然，對事實了解不足和不夠全面，最終只會誤導社會大眾。<br />\n<br />\n她指法院不時提及三權分立的概念，但終審法院或上訴委員會都沒有在相關案件中，嘗試就三權分立詳細討論。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊又引用時任高等法院原訟法庭法官夏正民曾用三權分立一詞，但同時強調了《基本法》中行政機關、行政當局及立法機關明顯地以互相協調，彼此合作的方式，為香港的良好管治各自履行其憲制上制定的角色。"},{"pid":"1a5200fd44343adf7eff504edfe8bef0018b0d07","tid":2195060,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=404868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404868&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=51997cdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404868&h=aa4f1112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=404868</a>"},{"pid":"60d7aff12a12338661a2067cee2bf649c8146012","tid":2195060,"uid":76135,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"wow, 台灣？"},{"pid":"2fa2ebe13dcf48b4441c6e5da347ab95e3bf2464","tid":2195060,"uid":59818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:36:19.000Z","msg":"話一直信奉三權分立班大狀係咪要轉做獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00eaa0cc2a95304e3a4bb7ae0707c467e1f8fc6","tid":2195060,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ia8ALlzijOc\" data-